id: pm-k9t17l
title: "GH-649: reject self-referential ordering relationships at the SDK mutation boundary"
description: "A create/update dependency mutation can persist a self blocked_by or inverse ordering edge that graph governance forbids, permanently removing the item from readiness while pm deps fails to identify the one-node cycle."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[6]: agent-ux,"area:graph","area:sdk",data-integrity,gh-issue,multi-agent
