comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:52:33.471Z",claude-code-agent,"Duplicate check 2026-07-23: all-status searches for GH-649,self-referential ordering edge,blocked_by self edge,and dependency cycle write guard found shipped cycle advisory pm-i6pi,governance lineage pm-6x7o/pm-ju83/pm-4jqm,and closed detection work pm-6irg,but no item owns the exact write-time self-edge inconsistency. Created this canonical leaf rather than reopening shipped work."
  "2026-07-23T04:53:29.272Z",claude-code-agent,"GitHub linkage evidence: canonical pm item posted on GH-649 at https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/649#issuecomment-5054564177. Active bundle shares the truthful-context lifecycle acceptance surface with pm-3esl28, pm-mmm9o5, and rolling SDK reference pm-ds3b."
  "2026-07-23T05:04:49.295Z",claude-code-agent,"TDD evidence: added failing SDK alias/allowSelf policy tests plus CLI create/update zero-write acceptance, then implemented one shared pre-persistence edge validator used by both mutation paths. Focused acceptance is green."
  "2026-07-23T05:30:02.577Z",claude-code-agent,"Live observability evidence: release gate identified Sentry PM-CLI-2J as the sole blocker. Sanitized issue facts: unresolved/high, handled TypeError from normalizeRelationshipEdge, 3 events, first/last seen 2026-07-22, all on release pm-cli@2026.7.22, no events after 2026-07-22T21:40:25Z. This implementation converts create/update self-edge attempts into deterministic usage errors before persistence; keep the Sentry issue unresolved until the merged release is verified, then resolve and rerun the gate."
  "2026-07-23T05:31:50.579Z",claude-code-agent,"Packed installed-consumer acceptance passed: public SDK custom allowSelf kind succeeded; CLI self dependency via depends-on exited usage=2 and created neither item nor history state. Real two-branch Git merge also retained both agents' notes. Evidence workspace: /tmp/tmp.9DpM65yUme."
  "2026-07-23T05:33:58.883Z",claude-code-agent,"Final local evidence: 6,101 tests at exact 100/100/100/100; all static/package/security/dogfood gates pass. Consolidated release gate's only red check is the pre-fix live Sentry issue PM-CLI-2J, deliberately retained until this fix ships."
